        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-367",
        "content": "Put this puree into a soup pot and finish by incorporating therewith the crawfish butter and season with a little cayenne pepper and the juice of half a lemon.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
