        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-367",
        "content": "IN WHICH ARE CONTAINED THE INNUMERABLE TROUBLES WHICH THE BRAVE DON QUIXOTE AND HIS GOOD SQUIRE SANCHO PANZA ENDURED IN THE INN, WHICH TO HIS MISFORTUNE HE TOOK TO BE A CASTLE",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
