        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/367/293981/367_293981_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-367",
        "content": "\"Thou mayest well believe that,\" answered Don Quixote, \"because, either I know little, or this castle is enchanted, for thou must know but this that I am now about to tell thee thou must swear to keep secret until after my death.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-367_293981_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/367/293981/367_293981_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-367",
        "content": "\"I say so,\" continued Don Quixote, \"because I hate taking away anyone's good name.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-367_293981_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/367/293981/367_293981_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-367",
        "content": "\"I say,\" replied Sancho, \"that I swear to hold my tongue about it till the end of your worship's days, and God grant I may be able to let it out tomorrow.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-367_293981_000010_000000",
