        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-367",
        "content": "\"It is not for that,\" replied Sancho, \"but because I hate keeping things long, and I don't want them to grow rotten with me from over keeping.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
