        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-367",
        "content": "Sancho Panza, who also regarded the amendment of his master as miraculous, begged him to give him what was left in the pigskin, which was no small quantity.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
